Class DictionaryHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.sukit.chatbot.DictionaryHandler

  • @Component
public class DictionaryHandler
extends java.lang.Object
    DictionaryHandler reads the data/dictionary.json-file into a String,String HashMap.

      • setDictionary

        public void setDictionary()
        Sets the dictionary-hashmap for this class by reading the data/dictionary.json-file into a JsonNode. Iterates through each JsonNode and writes the values of keyword and response into a new key-value-pair in the dictionary-hashmap. Said hashmap is then available via getDictionary().
